36:53.515 --> 36:55.430
[Vinsher]
There'’s too much rebel blood

36:55.474 --> 36:57.519
running through this planet.

36:57.563 --> 37:00.870
The last thing I need
is another Ha martyr.

37:00.914 --> 37:03.221
This must be done quietly
and discreetly.

37:03.960 --> 37:05.875
This requires a professional.

37:06.789 --> 37:08.661
You want me to handle it.

37:14.057 --> 37:16.364
[woman]
What the hell are you--? No!

37:18.323 --> 37:19.411
[grunts]

37:23.937 --> 37:25.373
-[gun cocks]
-[Soojin] Enough!

37:28.550 --> 37:30.335
-Kwan.
-Aunt Soojin.

37:32.337 --> 37:33.512
I heard rumors.

37:33.555 --> 37:35.383
Let me look at you.

37:35.427 --> 37:36.906
Auntie, we need your help.

37:36.950 --> 37:39.866
Kwan, you should not
have returned.

37:39.909 --> 37:41.694
Come with me quickly.

37:41.737 --> 37:42.956
You mustn'’t be seen.

37:42.999 --> 37:46.742
I'’ve worked very hard for this.

37:47.874 --> 37:49.789
I'’ve paid my dues.

37:49.832 --> 37:51.834
Played all the angles.

37:51.878 --> 37:53.749
It'’s my time.

38:03.933 --> 38:05.805
Fix this for me, Franco.

38:06.806 --> 38:08.808
I need to clean my ledger.

38:18.600 --> 38:19.688
In here.

38:22.691 --> 38:24.040
Stop.

38:24.084 --> 38:25.564
Are you sure you want
to go through

38:25.607 --> 38:27.043
all that embarrassment again?

38:27.087 --> 38:29.959
It'’s okay, Soren.
I'’m safe with Aunt Soojin.

38:31.613 --> 38:33.093
You get the money.

38:33.136 --> 38:36.444
I'’m gonna go see a man
about a ship.

38:43.016 --> 38:45.148
[Miranda]
