38:54.419 --> 38:56.986
Well, my mother
never let me near you.

38:57.030 --> 39:00.642
I always used to wonder
why she preferred you over me.

39:00.686 --> 39:03.123
I probably thought it was
'’cause you were more fun.

39:03.166 --> 39:05.343
That must have been
