39:09.651 --> 39:11.827
Uh, anyway, um...

39:11.871 --> 39:15.918
I'’m not getting a sense that fun
was a part of your training.

39:15.962 --> 39:17.920
-[Kai] Oh, we had fun.
-Oh, yeah?

39:17.964 --> 39:20.880
At one point
we were each given pets.

39:20.923 --> 39:23.535
I had a puppy. Cody.

39:23.578 --> 39:26.407
-Riz, you had a cat.
-Eloise.

39:27.539 --> 39:28.627
You'’re kidding.

39:28.670 --> 39:31.412
Vannak, you had a pig.

39:31.456 --> 39:32.587
-Ivan.
-Ivan.

39:32.631 --> 39:34.676
Ivan the Terrible.

39:34.720 --> 39:37.810
See, we were studying
the strategies of the wolf pack.

39:37.853 --> 39:39.942
And Dr. Halsey would make teams.

39:39.986 --> 39:42.597
The hunted
and the hunters.

39:42.641 --> 39:44.425
Sounds like a blast.

39:44.469 --> 39:46.166
[Kai]
Two days in the woods,

39:46.209 --> 39:48.864
tracking, eating whatever
you could find,

39:48.908 --> 39:51.127
and stalking
and killing your prey.

39:51.171 --> 39:53.869
Whichever side failed
lost their pets.

39:54.957 --> 39:56.742
What, she took them
away from you?

39:56.785 --> 39:59.527
No. She had us eliminate them.

40:02.617 --> 40:03.836
[scoffs]
Come on.

40:03.879 --> 40:06.491
Every failure carries
consequences.

40:06.534 --> 40:09.624
I was on the winning side
nine times before I lost.

40:09.668 --> 40:11.757
I failed on my third mission.

40:11.800 --> 40:13.585
[Vannak]
I never lost.

40:13.628 --> 40:16.588
So you got to keep Ivan.

40:16.631 --> 40:18.894
Dr. Halsey eliminated it.

40:18.938 --> 40:21.854
Spartans must be bonded
to one another,

40:21.897 --> 40:23.508
and nothing else.

40:38.261 --> 40:41.830
I warned you triggering memories
from your past

40:41.874 --> 40:43.963
would destabilize you.

40:44.006 --> 40:46.879
I'’m now concerned that...

40:46.922 --> 40:48.533
that you'’re having visions

40:48.576 --> 40:50.926
even when you'’re not
in the presence of the artifact.

40:50.970 --> 40:53.102
We need to get you home

40:53.146 --> 40:54.800
so we can study
the drawings--

40:54.843 --> 40:56.976
[John]
I saw you.

40:58.325 --> 41:00.240
I was a boy.

41:00.283 --> 41:02.024
And you were with me.

41:03.243 --> 41:05.898
-Of course I was with you--
-[John] No.

41:05.941 --> 41:08.553
Not at the orphanage. Here.

41:08.596 --> 41:09.858
In my house.

41:09.902 --> 41:12.078
My parents
