41:14.950 --> 41:16.865
Why were you here?

41:16.909 --> 41:18.040
It'’s natural.

41:18.084 --> 41:19.564
Memories get muddled,

41:19.607 --> 41:21.609
particularly where
trauma'’s involved.

41:21.653 --> 41:27.006
You were so young when we met,
and so overwhelmed with grief.

41:27.049 --> 41:29.530
I took care of you.

41:30.966 --> 41:34.013
I have been with you ever since,

41:34.056 --> 41:36.232
and I am still here
for you now.

41:51.857 --> 41:53.728
[indistinct chatter]

42:08.177 --> 42:10.702
-Well?
-Bad news, friend.

42:10.745 --> 42:12.573
What do you mean, bad news?

42:12.617 --> 42:15.271
