42:22.757 --> 42:24.716
Those filthy animals.

42:24.759 --> 42:27.283
If you'’re looking for
the fastest way off Madrigal,

42:27.327 --> 42:30.939
transport ships take off
every night for New Carthage

42:30.983 --> 42:33.246
