Solar Time.

42:34.769 --> 42:36.292
Where do these ships
take off from?

42:36.336 --> 42:40.209
Granada, 200 miles due south.

42:42.385 --> 42:44.692
-Two hundred miles?
-Through the desert.

42:44.736 --> 42:48.217
For the, uh, right price
I can take you there.

42:51.656 --> 42:53.745
Hmm.

42:54.963 --> 42:56.225
That'’s a nice lid.

42:57.487 --> 42:59.707
Real stylish.

43:04.973 --> 43:07.106
I'’ll take the bike too.

43:10.675 --> 43:13.112
Dad started with only
50 fighters.

43:13.155 --> 43:15.810
We can find at least that many,
and with the family'’s money--

43:15.854 --> 43:17.638
There is nothing left, Kwan.

43:17.682 --> 43:20.336
