so did the people.

43:22.861 --> 43:25.864
They'’re scared
and they'’re desperate,

43:25.907 --> 43:27.169
but we can beat Vinsher.

43:27.213 --> 43:28.431
The people just need
to be reminded

43:28.475 --> 43:30.782
of what they were
fighting for.

43:30.825 --> 43:33.915
Come. My men will get you
out of town safely

43:33.959 --> 43:35.351
and you will stay far away--

43:35.395 --> 43:37.789
I can'’t let him down.

43:37.832 --> 43:39.094
He died to save me.

43:39.138 --> 43:40.792
I have to pick up
where he left off.

43:40.835 --> 43:42.968
No! I will not allow it.

43:43.011 --> 43:44.926
I can fight just as he did.

43:44.970 --> 43:47.146
Your father
fought for a lie!

43:48.190 --> 43:50.149
What are you talking about?

43:52.847 --> 43:56.285
I never wanted to ruin your
father'’s image in your heart.

43:57.809 --> 43:59.114
Tell me.

44:02.291 --> 44:05.251
Years ago,
before the war,

44:05.294 --> 44:07.819
your father visited
a group in the desert.

44:09.385 --> 44:10.778
Mystics.

44:10.822 --> 44:13.868
When he returned,

44:13.912 --> 44:15.696
everything was different.

44:15.740 --> 44:17.132
[grunts]

44:18.003 --> 44:19.265
He was different.

44:20.266 --> 44:22.007
What did they tell him?

44:22.050 --> 44:24.009
He never said.

44:24.052 --> 44:27.708
But he returned convinced
it was his responsibility

44:27.752 --> 44:29.275
to free Madrigal.

44:29.318 --> 44:31.843
He told me it was the only way
for the Ha family'’s

44:31.886 --> 44:33.714
true purpose to be revealed.

44:33.758 --> 44:35.107
What true purpose?

44:35.150 --> 44:38.719
Our real reason
for being on Madrigal,

44:38.763 --> 44:40.329
and the reason we fight,

44:40.373 --> 44:43.158
according to the desert people.

44:44.159 --> 44:45.813
And he believed them.

44:45.857 --> 44:48.860
Your father believed
what he wanted to believe.

44:50.035 --> 44:52.037
Where can I find these mystics?

44:52.080 --> 44:53.778
-Kwan, no.
-[thud]

44:55.214 --> 44:56.781
What was that?

45:01.481 --> 45:03.091
Kwan, go!

45:03.135 --> 45:05.006
[grunts]

45:05.050 --> 45:06.399
Hello, Kwan.

45:06.442 --> 45:07.748
[panting]

45:07.792 --> 45:08.923
What are you doing here?

45:08.967 --> 45:10.403
Cleaning up
your father'’s mess.

45:10.446 --> 45:12.753
As usual.
Where'’s your friend?

45:14.146 --> 45:17.062
-[shouts]
-[grunts]

45:17.105 --> 45:19.064
Aunt Soojin!

45:19.107 --> 45:21.240
-No!
-[blood splatters]

45:22.807 --> 45:24.199
[Soren]
Hey!

45:29.161 --> 45:30.510
[grunts]

45:33.905 --> 45:36.734
[sobbing]
Aunt Soojin.

45:37.647 --> 45:40.433
Shit! Never should have
left the Rubble.

45:40.476 --> 45:42.130
[bullet casings clatter]

45:42.174 --> 45:44.176
Cost me my ship too.
Come on.

45:44.219 --> 45:48.876
We'’re about to have Vinsher's
entire army on our ass.

45:52.140 --> 45:54.012
[crying]

45:54.055 --> 45:55.274
Come on.

45:55.317 --> 45:56.579
Let'’s go.

45:59.234 --> 46:01.323
[indistinct chattering]

46:03.499 --> 46:04.979
-[gunshots]
-Stay down!

46:05.023 --> 46:06.328
[screams and shouts]

46:13.945 --> 46:15.250
Go! Go! Go!

46:15.294 --> 46:17.862
[engine revs]

46:17.905 --> 46:19.994
[automatic gunfire]

46:20.038 --> 46:21.822
[indistinct shouting]

46:21.866 --> 46:23.519
[woman screams]

46:36.315 --> 46:38.404
-Behind you.
-[gunshot]

46:38.447 --> 46:39.535
Go!

46:45.933 --> 46:47.021
Dr. Halsey.

46:48.196 --> 46:49.894
[Adun grunts]

46:49.937 --> 46:52.853
Cortana'’s analysis of
Master Chief'’s brain scans

46:52.897 --> 46:54.159
from earlier today.

46:54.202 --> 46:56.117
Hmm.

46:56.161 --> 46:57.989
I mean, you were right.

46:58.032 --> 47:01.601
He'’s reopened neural clusters
in his amygdala.

47:04.517 --> 47:06.954
Yeah, emotions mixed
with memory.

47:06.998 --> 47:08.173
Yeah.

47:08.216 --> 47:10.349
And it'’s impossible to determine

47:10.392 --> 47:12.568
what'’s hidden
in any given neural cluster,

47:12.612 --> 47:15.528
so there'’s no way of knowing
exactly what he remembered.

47:15.571 --> 47:17.269
[footsteps approaching]

47:20.968 --> 47:22.927
[John]
I remember.

47:24.493 --> 47:26.495
The second object is here...

47:27.453 --> 47:29.020
on Eridanus.

47:30.412 --> 47:31.936
And I know where it is.

47:40.335 --> 47:43.251
[engine revs]

47:47.429 --> 47:51.085
[garbled voices speaking
Sangheili over computer]

47:53.348 --> 47:55.263
[Kai]
Stop it right there.

47:55.307 --> 47:57.526
Yeah, what--
what do you have for that?

47:57.570 --> 47:59.964
At first I had "foundation,"

48:00.007 --> 48:02.967
but that other syllable
changes it, doesn'’t it?

48:03.010 --> 48:04.142
[Kai]
Yeah.

48:04.185 --> 48:05.926
Oq-- Oq'’ogakha.

48:05.970 --> 48:08.407
It'’s, uh,
"keystone," maybe?

48:09.277 --> 48:11.018
[Miranda] Could that
be the artifact?

48:11.062 --> 48:14.282
Do you have access
to the HUD data from the cave?

48:14.326 --> 48:16.545
Yeah, um, hold on.

48:16.589 --> 48:18.634
[computer chirping]

48:21.246 --> 48:23.596
You haven'’t been completely
honest with me.

48:27.208 --> 48:28.949
What-- What do you mean?

48:30.995 --> 48:32.344
My hair.

48:32.387 --> 48:33.998
It'’s awful.

48:35.086 --> 48:37.044
-[laughs] No.
-I just don'’t know

48:37.088 --> 48:38.611
what came over me.

48:38.654 --> 48:42.049
A small act of rebellion,
maybe, against Halsey.

48:42.093 --> 48:44.965
Well, against
a lot of things, maybe.

48:45.009 --> 48:46.488
[laughs]

48:46.532 --> 48:48.969
[John, over video]
Retrieving now.

48:57.456 --> 48:59.110
[garbled voice speaks Sangheili]

48:59.153 --> 49:00.502
-Wow.
-What?

49:00.546 --> 49:03.592
This word, from the Sangheili
broadcast.

49:03.636 --> 49:05.638
Ch'’anggagomo.

49:08.162 --> 49:10.208
I have "sacred ring."

49:10.251 --> 49:11.557
Look.

49:13.124 --> 49:14.386
Sacred ring.

49:16.475 --> 49:18.564
"Halo."

49:24.352 --> 49:27.312
Do you think that'’s what
the Covenant are talking about?

49:27.355 --> 49:29.270
Uh...

49:29.314 --> 49:32.404
I know that you report
directly to Halsey, but...

49:32.447 --> 49:35.537
can we just keep this
between us?

49:35.581 --> 49:38.062
At least for now, until
I figure out what all this--

49:38.105 --> 49:39.150
Yeah, no problem.

49:40.629 --> 49:42.370
It'’s our secret.

49:42.414 --> 49:45.286
You know, the way I see it,

49:45.330 --> 49:48.028
we'’re sort of like sisters.

49:48.072 --> 49:49.247
[chuckles]

49:49.290 --> 49:51.727
I gotta say,
Petty Officer...

49:53.164 --> 49:55.427
there'’s something
very odd about you.

49:56.558 --> 49:58.038
Ma'’am?

50:00.084 --> 50:01.520
[Miranda]
Dr. Halsey designed everything

50:01.563 --> 50:03.130
to her specifications.

50:04.610 --> 50:07.395
When her creations
behave in unexpected ways,

50:07.439 --> 50:09.615
she gets uncomfortable.

50:11.356 --> 50:15.621
Well, what does it mean
to behave in unexpected ways?

50:16.665 --> 50:18.798
Like a human...

50:18.841 --> 50:20.147
I suppose.

50:23.194 --> 50:26.327
To Dr. Halsey,
human beings are messy,

50:26.371 --> 50:28.199
irrational, chaotic.

50:28.242 --> 50:32.768
They make decisions
based on emotion, passion.

50:44.432 --> 50:47.131
Halsey is different.

50:47.174 --> 50:48.871
She sees the world
as a set of data

50:48.915 --> 50:50.743
to be optimized, regardless

50:50.786 --> 50:53.702
of the short-term pain
or sacrifice.

50:59.969 --> 51:01.667
Next to this level
of dedication,

51:01.710 --> 51:03.843
the rest of us
ultimately fall short.

51:10.676 --> 51:13.287
And when people let her down,

51:13.331 --> 51:16.638
Dr. Halsey has a way
of cutting them

51:16.682 --> 51:18.510
out of her life.

51:18.553 --> 51:21.513
But Halsey never stops.

51:21.556 --> 51:23.341
She just keeps pushing forward,

51:23.384 --> 51:26.735
determined to bend us towards
her vision of the future.

51:27.867 --> 51:29.869
She'’s convinced
there'’s something out there

51:29.912 --> 51:31.871
just beyond our reach.

51:33.960 --> 51:36.658
An answer to our
eternal questions.

51:36.702 --> 51:38.443
Who are we?

51:38.486 --> 51:41.315
Where are we heading?
What is our true potential?

51:51.499 --> 51:54.633
She'’s dedicated her life's work
to finding those answers.

51:56.809 --> 51:58.854
And she'’ll never give up...

52:00.943 --> 52:02.815
no matter the cost.

52:04.295 --> 52:08.168
Kai, your act of rebellion
could just be a glitch.

52:12.694 --> 52:14.696
But if I know Dr. Halsey...

52:24.924 --> 52:27.361
she doesn'’t tolerate glitches.

52:31.626 --> 52:35.674
[end theme music plays]
